  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Place</strong> a wide-based pan (ideally non-stick and with a matching lid) over a medium-high heat with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(2 tbsp)</span> vegetable oil</p>\r\n<p><strong>When</strong> hot, add the chicken and colour on each side for 3 min or until golden</p>\r\n<p><strong>Season</strong> each side generously with salt&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Once</strong> golden, add a splash of water (approx. 2-3 tbsp) and cover immediately with a lid (stand back as it will spit!)</p>\r\n<p>Tip: The trapped water creates steam for even cooking</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reduce</strong> the heat to medium-low and cook for a further 7-10 min or until the chicken is cooked through, lowering the heat if necessary</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, boil a kettle for step 5</p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong> and cut the carrots into bite-size pieces, discarding the root ends</p>\r\n<p><strong>Trim </strong>the green beans and cut them in half widthways</p>\r\n<p><strong>Soak</strong> the coconut cream sachet<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> in a bowl of very hot water (this softens it)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Once</strong> the chicken is cooked, transfer it to a clean chopping board and allow to rest for 5 min</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the carrot to the same pan with a large pinch of salt</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook</strong> over a medium-high heat for 3 min or until coloured and caramelised</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/476.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
