          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, add the green beans to the caramelised carrots and cover again with a lid</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook</strong> for 5 min over a medium-low heat or until both vegetables are tender&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, peel and chop (or grate) the garlic finely</p>",
